A-FiyfV-fd1HfOv3/9" target="_blank"&gt;包括Google在内的&lt;/a&gt;多家技术公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tNMHLoBR1h9r8_91KaMVhkIC8928wR1iaqg4U95yUOhLrnIbSB--yi20jGW465I5mtQMZfWQ0zb7AW73I8Jem-lMRJ-O7FW6r2fDiqRKqU1aPCZyOv6Auty3CE3wncPfRfVdqYSbcrQ3w3X-0LqGTyb3GcArgv56bb74WUKfKzgKXfjR8QxFcEiqaNXWQTB8nsvTQ_lM8Gq0wvbzpl30oS73o0132LdRFgaYjzT2ejMTVuoKKS-AnWRDeX_o3bsxxN5K8_grbJZ6Lo79xWyzF8Q-KA/L57UtfqFG2obUEwKMCOLBGp0SkhJVqN2/9" target="_blank"&gt;偷猎顶级工程师&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;座位11a的奇迹。&lt;/strong&gt; 40岁的英国公民Ramesh Vishwaskumar讲述了他是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cd_beiwmd9PL_goi6TX6VGKTG0tw-XBY3s7DhCJHfaCmHwBUssFi06H4hMFUMqlAc7oBol78aTNuPsGODLClJonAO3ghVl33jctwYuBpngPZtk4SVRHrydEqyERE3a51XARjwvi4mXxOT9942ytdCLUrFHk096hlOceNhLmn3PihNk24jM2ckkTx5tv-nP9nXambxgbHlIAGy6VHjVylhUqX8hTJcqm59Xtf3Mu1pLFqlIianMtJTvoWXrCdzJeXuDV_uNd37QQbp4zzcxj6ia4Lyw/ZEGnRcqSiiH7Plr7A-EPp8u3mIUkXwvo/9" target="_blank"&gt;印度航空AI171航班的唯一幸存者&lt;/a&gt;的故事。他坐在第一行经济舱中，设法穿过飞机侧面破的门逃脱。十年来，这次坠机事故在最致命的航空事故中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bf4snV8w3TNvZHVr5MMhH7qYs08YUNf27S7DIsjEzaDF-OGNhBnANEPYhdhgzwya1DUdxt0_qXvhXmwFHS-XhmLgaMYs-rdOOjaLCqk0yGB0xwbIIzarS7bBQG2PfSEAq9eWBn1EUV6JHTJ3qTLlwDeYQIcZYs_848Zqp49yoR_kruCjyL3cDx1jroqYbDUy0AZAh4rS5YMWpI1dgse42ahML8XZiR0Q-PCoq443d6YEayEQSFeISXwu2o-DammVncEaRQ5YGLn8b3mOQbwu1CikPw/3EJlhAlXR8uSaVi0hdm5PBoztULo6xV4/9" target="_blank"&gt;杀死了241名乘客&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt; Big Take Podcast &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;