llapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;对中东最新升级的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;最明显市场反应&lt;/strong&gt;是石油。如果持续增长，能源价格将成为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/C6CDpbw-IGYnBMIKAPyttAf_OLbeCUE2TSTsPJGOmWaX4WZGeobEjqne3dNvfAfTiO0H7lOekH4_jQhRRoAygOI5l8hjZdyjEEKX4cGHE45alKoXjqTjvFyGTO_P7e2RMHstmFJgP1MAw4dyuwvphAwzhK1EEtkrza4MwNyAt1q4WLWCaAyloHdZNMLPv4Xrl8J6FCxHPCUk2_qczq6cbeEDr-xt21ek8NlJZFARDjb2E-JD2b8AIqgkuCERp2gEPDpJQSqrk4QWLZKPmBkIyMMcMg/IFR4flHO2j7wNoZ2Om0O9uyDMKamGN9D/9" target="_blank"&gt;全球经济和特朗普总统的另一个逆风&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;更昂贵的石油&lt;/strong&gt;及其副产品将增加美国关税的通货膨胀冲动，并且&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4I1TsPHkZYrYhu8I28Ilj3d-dsGYAWFLmcIe_t-gj-NzS_Qhc5gnxs-iN5QmWLjTffpj3mAOrJloNgA3sD7okFqpMbRd-juHXL0-vXrKrQ29bjJucRoWkFfeEMiA0mIekyLSegokgfnRNFcyuOdAKrPx0nEb9-sZp9r5yKuyUYTHBn6AOaqle-bzwvz1pnaw8jpJUeKwpQDMFfr7j3f7_UpaIkjEwL8tW7TA2blAqcmW9-i2fTCtUKqx9y12svqWWZe9jZyPtxsljgk2O17SUFYapw/MMNYvuty47ThtBtCc9vuPD8Lbesfa17U/9" target="_blank"&gt;中央银行很难&lt;/a&gt;忽略，可能会影响利率的前景。特朗普在要求降低借贷成本时特别发声。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;自2022年以来，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;石油选择&lt;/strong&gt;升至他们最看涨的人，而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7f6eqfBxVjXKuDQByGn2-MIE82PPbmpVAbyHRZ-kfyXyGo4qYraGj-Zt_2h6tOE3XBJycAZ4o1KKWpp8BFsq8iMOvPl0ciR-L-zr2yyMaIs6Lc87j1J0qS0ar_YGjyDa_XpCP8KDAud78FWPHyi3Mg_42LlVWQJk-TryNxzOc1FdvMwkiLfGGLcxOqKpzhXZUKTemcJmSTGj4gAFKs9px8nc8qPVHEksBZBMIY8Eom-ut4YdZQOfXc5kOXAAQMTrmdxc6PeTItvJzKBHd87PjrNpqg/iIemMX28Ql08cES1AUzhQBkPUH0D2CcM/9" target="_blank"&gt;石油期货曲线正在加强&lt;/a&gt;人们对以色列对伊朗的最新罢工可能会产生严重且持久的影响的担忧。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;本周早些时候&lt;/strong&gt;，摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase）的分析师表示，在通过Hormuz海峡或中东发生更广泛的大火中，价格可能会达到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cdGV2JkhNo0fC-tS2AwwS635CFZ-T1kKhXvFZhf7WPPs5BQsUEWQGIYZOhRID9mcO-PG2glGAOj5eUdpQyBRWLIOjB-5Fz4N7UynbYzXXI7w0PNvW6U6wnZBa7SfGXJomPqDd0MfLK85HIkPd-YUqdxqe203hrvEyEwKammwkPtljgORGQs35p8sjNSI3CAgeBQ-IqkWpkbb1qdXfCFaAb3UeRH84g9gu3X53XFVE35nJ27MQiZSxqcy6fU0Vphx2ZecQdwPEqF35fq8Uv1eNNPgFA/zmKrEBfI7A___LkwT6gLuQC9OxD-vVmW/9" target="_blank"&gt;每桶130美元&lt;/a&gt;的桶装。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;运输市场&lt;/strong&gt;也承受着压力。世界上最大的石油潮流运营商之一说，现在，它“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9A57fLsUEobeh_pcmj9E1HhATeN2rhQdWIi8enDt3faZRuttaux-yp8dQZgGHclwjaqA1Xw7MyCNlx0Xb-9l59DthhgNIBmH2p8MBMM3foZ9plTwJ-wEUdQLDtfbqsYjzBkRYo87l_wT7jijW0KH8gs16Ha7sxnOH_mHTjeogMvgfRbZlnm_-IBv7XPezcojxUbkw0P1kJUHRtnVwK6rRvlvP7D4qeeL31oF3Cb_LpBIwjlcXDw9nx3RaFETBywGr_HKL18X_wJa211AurLpCCNb0Q/7JSZl5V3_NCigCVoTvDezX-u7MvWo6OA/9" target="_blank"&gt;更加犹豫&lt;/a&gt;”在罢工之后提供其船只从海湾运送货物的船只。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WBVypgkjrq_Loz7arVtU8wi8zTo5YgpWqlupp_jFeGa_qTJBCVlQuG2KTyzwEyCVTqk5if_dFwYVj4j3njFT2WEvma51vUvoqruttgrIhYKQgcjWKQx1epaPHufkq_ry_x_kKwtt46PUuJYzofNrGC-oVNVgezD2fPzZWNhxVGi_TFPABFahBrgRNvKsZPfC5VZ3jqe1_KOMnMOWiuSulvzx0MdfZujbdciSd_34PgpgMIYVzuFym6Aos8BFFFVo4jtLd5yOb7IzzRWzPiBpTZLUXw/wp6wGBkSsWEQyIsSDXfedc9aCOacPq5g/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iGvbAF5kA6tM/v0/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div s